Package my.data_structures

Class BinarySearchTree<V>

java.lang.Object
my.data_structures.BinarySearchTree<V>
Type Parameters:
V - value corresponding to keys
public class BinarySearchTree<V>
extends java.lang.Object
An implementation of Binary Search Tree with int keys, <V> values, and optional int weights (i.e. search frequencies) for optimal BST.
Author:
Jiale Hu
